@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/Index.css">
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home page";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title></title>

<style>

body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}

.feature-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
}

.feature-box {
        flex: 1; /* Equal width for each box */
        max-width: 300px; /* Maximum width for each box */
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 10px;
}

footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f2f2f2;
}

    .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 25px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        margin: 10px;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    #signup {
        background-color: #3b3b3b; /* Black */
        color: #fff;
    }

    #login {
        background-color: #8b572a; /* Brown */
        color: #fff;
    }
    
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4">Pet Reunion Hub</h1>
        <h2>Aid and Grief Support for Missing or Departed Pets</h2>
        <p>In Pet Reunion Hub, we reunite pets and their owners, both physically and emotionally, for pets who have either gone missing or passed away. Pets weave a thread of companionship, offering unwavering loyalty and joy. Anticipating the grief associated with a lost pet or navigating the acute sorrow of a departed companion can be challenging.</p>
        <p>Feel free to use this platform to report your missing pets or to honour and remember your beloved companions while finding the support you need. You can count on this website as a virtual memory box, enabling you to store photos or written tributes about your departed companion, accessible from any device at any time. Here, we recognise that every pet holds a special place in your heart, there is no such thing as "it's just a dog" or "it's just a spider".</p>
        <p>We invite you to let this be your safe space to seek assistance in lost pet reporting as well as preserve memories of your cherished pets and share them with the community, fostering a sense of support among one another.</p>

        <h2 class="display-5">Our Offers</h2>


        <div class="feature-container">

            <div class="feature-box">
                <h2>Lost Pet Reporting</h2>
                <p>Our Lost Pet Reporting feature provides a streamlined and compassionate platform to report missing pets. Whether your furry friend has wandered off or is lost, utilize this tool to swiftly document crucial information, aiding in a quicker reunion.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box">
                <h2>Pet Memorial</h2>
                <p>Capture the essence of your cherished companions with our Pet Memorial feature. Create a lasting tribute by sharing your pet's unique story, photos, and videos. This virtual memorial allows you to celebrate the joy your pet brought into your life and provides a space for others to connect through shared memories.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box">
                <h2>Grief Support</h2>
                <p>In times of grief, our Grief Support feature offers a curated collection of coping resources. From counseling services to memorial customization, discover a range of tools to navigate the emotional journey of losing a pet. Access literature, testimonies, and personalized recommendations to find solace and support.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h3>Welcome to Pet Reunion Hub!</h3>
        <p>We're thrilled to have you join our community dedicated to reuniting pets and providing support during challenging times. By signing up, you'll have access to exclusive features and the ability to store your progress, making it easier to navigate through the platform.</p>

        <h4 class="display-6"></h4>
        <a href="/signup" id="signup" class="button">Sign Up</a>
        <a href="/login" id="login" class="button">Log In</a>



    </div>

    <footer>
        <!-- "About Us" and "Contact Us" links styled as buttons -->
        <a href="/AboutUs" class="button about-us">About Us</a>
        <a href="/Contact" class="button contact-us">Contact Us</a>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>